    <note>Yu(9) Ruli [2098] XNYL, 137.12b, 141.13a; SHY:ZG, 70.24a; Sichuan TZ, 122.50a. Chen Liang, WJ, 28.8a traces the origin of the Wuzhou, Yiwu Yu(9) to Lingjing jian in Sichuan. I will, therefore, treat them as jia 'b' and Ruli and his immediate kin as jia 'a' of zu #889. It is interesting to note that there are important He(2) lineages in both Yiwu and Lingjing and that the Yiwu He and Yu are members of the same kindred group. CBD, 4, 2966-7.</note>
